  "body": "<p>Here's another installation of awesome projects designed by talented crafters using my Plus One Collection. This includes the awesome flowers and wreath shown in the segment featuring the <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/products/amy-tangerine-plus-one-papercrafting-kit/7407018\">paper crafting kit</a>. The Delicate Construction tutorial can be found <a href=\"http://delicateconstruction.com/2014/03/spring-paper-flower-wreath-amytangerine.html\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598771091251-EBO2BDPYAHNLVQMTF7Y6/1a-amytangerine-4.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Spring Paper Flower Wreath by <a href=\"http://delicateconstruction.com/2014/03/spring-paper-flower-wreath-amytangerine.html\">Delicate Construction</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598771106882-2662UDYAMSK76B1CIOE8/1b-spring-wreath-8-600x560.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Spring Pinwheel Wreath by <a href=\"http://www.diapers-n-heels.com/spring-pinwheel-wreath/\">Diapers-N-Heels</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598771122722-8TQEMLSNL76ROT7FMCDW/1c-embroidered-paper-used-in-scrap-booking-600x581.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Embroidered Paper by <a href=\"http://www.dosmallthingswithlove.com/2014/03/embroidering-paper-amy-tangerine.html\">Do Small Things with Love</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598771146405-7OMA79QV49LGS33X30I7/1d-DIY_To_Do_Board_Vertical-487x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>DIY To-Do Board by <a href=\"http://www.playpartypin.com/2014/03/diy-to-do-board.html\">Play. Party. Pin.</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598771170554-SVSILNGW6QYBEGUB3IEY/1e-Amy-Tangerine-Whittles-6195wm-398x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Papercrafting Projects by <a href=\"http://www.pnpflowersinc.com/2014/03/Amy-Tangerine-Papercrafting-Projects.html\">Pen N' Paper Flowers</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598771187624-A3COT52GZ2TK7ZU0YIWU/1f-Mini-Using-American-Crafts-and-Amy-Tangerine-600x418.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Instagram Mini Album by <a href=\"http://www.makelifelovely.com/2014/03/instagram-mini-album-using-amy.html\">Make Life Lovely</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>You can still get your hands on some of the discounted bundles <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/search?query=amy%20tangerine\">on HSN</a>.</p><p>In case you missed the any of the previous Plus One project posts, here's <a href=\"https://amy-tan-z6av.squarespace.com/amy-tangerine/2014/03/plus-one-on-hsn.html\">Part One</a>, <a href=\"https://amy-tan-z6av.squarespace.com/amy-tangerine/2014/03/plus-one-collection-for-hsn-projects-part-two.html\">Part Two</a>, and <a href=\"https://amy-tan-z6av.squarespace.com/amy-tangerine/2014/03/plus-one-collection-for-hsn-part-three.html\">Part Three</a> and the <a href=\"https://amy-tan-z6av.squarespace.com/\">wrap up</a>.</p>"
